      title: 'Conversation Design and Safety',
      duration: 'Weeks 4 to 7',
      description: 'We design the conversational behaviour, tone and fallback handling, and build the safety layer: input/output filtering, prompt-injection defences, topic boundaries and PII handling. The assistant is tuned to refuse out-of-scope requests gracefully and to know its limits.',
